You have to be more patient, my son.

87
00:06:08,083 --> 00:06:10,916
I'm almost done
with the new version of the amulet.

88
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,750
You will have it within this year.

89
00:06:12,833 --> 00:06:15,458
