179
00:10:03,583 --> 00:10:05,041
-Sun Rong.
-Yes.

180
00:10:05,125 --> 00:10:07,958
I'll give you five votes
for five packs of dry noodles.

181
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:09,791
{\an8}<i>At this point, Wang Ling</i>

182
00:10:10,541 --> 00:10:11,541
